entries.femaleVariant: Lookin' for somethin' raw, untouched.
Whaddaya lookin' for?
Raw's all you get with me. What's your edge?
Want somethin' that'll floor me, really scramble the neurons.
What's this one do?
Yeah, I can see that...
Need a special braindance.
We've got it all, man. Bare-knuckle boxing, shootouts, black ops interrogations, amputations…
Looking for a special kind of braindance.
Lookin' for somethin' special. A braindance to really…
Lookin' for BDs. A particular kind.
Nah... I mean something like... Well, y'know.
You mean… smut?
Particular...?
Fetishes?
No. C'mon, you know what I mean.
No, I don't. Think I'd be doin' this job if I could read minds?
Wanna know what it's like to... kill somebody.
See? Wasn't so hard. So, got some classics from the last corp war, or armed robbery if you're lookin' for something fresher.
Use your imagination.
Why do you think I came here? So I wouldn't have to...
Ahem. You chosen something?
Nah. More hardcore.
Won't find it here. But there's a guy on Jig-Jig Street has a whole lotta peculiar flicks, and I mean peculiar...
Lookin' for a woman.
Where do you get these scrolls?
If I was a badge, you'd already be in cuffs for what you sold the customer before me.
You a badge?
Cops are like kids – mommy and daddy wouldn't let 'em go off on their lonesome.
All right, all right, can't be too careful.
What do you want?
Gimme the best of the best. Ones with the Death's Head.
Want the kind with the Death's Head badge.
Hmm... Didn't know I was dealin' with a connoisseur. Death's Head'll cost ya, though.
[Browse items] What've you got?
No discount?
How 'bout a discount for your newest customer?
Only give regulars discounts. If you're short, then fuck off.
Said you weren't a pig.
Just curious, that's all.
Once you've booted up your virtu, daresay your curiosity will be satisfied.
Lookin' for a ripperdoc goes by Fingers. Heard of him?
Fingers, Fingers... Sets off a buzzer, tell you that much.
Know where I can find him?
Not a clue in the world.
See a woman here with blue hair? Young, total knock-out?
Y'know, you're the first person I've seen in months who actually fits that description.
entries.maleVariant: My customers're mostly uglier. Usually of the old, male-pattern balding variety.

entries.femaleVariant: If I'd seen a young, knock-out chick, I'd remember her. Gonna remember you, too, heheh.
entries.maleVariant: If I'd seen a young, knock-out chick, I'd remember her. Just like you do, prolly, heheh.

entries.femaleVariant: People that make these? OBSESSED with privacy.
Never even occurred to me to ask where they're from. To which caution I prolly owe the fact that I'm still alive, talkin' to you.
I'm no connoisseur.
I'm no connoisseur, trust me.
Hm, sure.
All I need to know is who makes 'em… and where.
Now listen, I just sell whatever sells. Nice, calm job. Lemme see some eddies, you can pick one, parse it, an' I won't care a hair.
What've you got?
Virtus.
Any special kind?
Lemme put it to you this way – those who know, don't need to ask.
Cops don't go out alone around here.
Cop would have enough evidence to detain already.
Where do you get your goods?
I'll come back some other time…
What're you selling?
How 'bout you? Ya buyin' or just gonna stand there like a pig undercover?
Bettin' on it.
Where'll I find Fingers?
Pleasure doin' biz with ya.
Whaddaya got?
Got anything that might interest me?
How can I be of service?
